    <h4 style="font-weight:bold; font-size: 17px;">Please double check the time of the lab classes that you will tutor on the <a href="https://timetable.dundee.ac.uk/Scientia/SWS/Dundee1617/" target="_blank">official timetable</a> or make direct contact with the lecturers through provided emails.</h4>
